<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00027</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING INCENTIVES TO PUBLIC SCHOOL TEACHERS WHO ARE ASSIGNED OUTSIDE OF THEIR TOWNS AND PROVINCES, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides that any public school teacher who is assigned to a town other than his own shall be entitled to Two Thousand Pesos (P2,000.00) monthly incentive allowance; and those who are assigned to a town of another province, other than their own, shall receive Four Thousand Pesos (P4,000.00) monthly incentive allowance.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Public School Teachers’ Incentive Act.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ESCUDERO, EVELINA G.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Ramos (000 2019-08-05)</td><td>2. Madrona (000 2019-08-06)</td><tr><td>3. De Venecia (000 2019-08-14)</td><td>4. Dalipe (000 2019-08-20)</td><tr><td>5. Fortun (000 2019-08-28)</td><td>6. Sy-Alvarado (000 2019-09-10)</td><tr><td>7. Savellano (000 2019-09-11)</td><td>8. Nieto (000 2019-09-12)</td><tr><td>9. Dy (F.) (000 2019-09-16)</td><td>10. Pancho (000 2019-09-24)</td><tr><td>11. Tan (S.A.) (000 2020-02-04)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON BASIC EDUCATION AND CULTURE ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>